14:43.414 --> 14:45.297
if you're dressed as a
famous couple from history.

14:45.332 --> 14:46.348
Please, please, please?

14:46.399 --> 14:48.200
Uh, well, won't me going
with you make Danny...

14:48.234 --> 14:49.335
Yeah. Yeah, exactly.

14:49.386 --> 14:52.204
And that's what us
girlfriends call a win-win.

14:53.656 --> 14:55.591
No, no, no. I can't. I can't.

