my... You get the point.

15:06.419 --> 15:07.403
You know what?

15:07.454 --> 15:09.338
That's genius!

15:09.372 --> 15:10.472
Yes, yes! I will go with you!

15:10.507 --> 15:11.690
Okay. Yay!

15:11.725 --> 15:14.326
