we can do at the last minute?

15:14.377 --> 15:16.428
Um, I've got a black
wig and some 60s clothes.

15:16.479 --> 15:17.429
Sonny and Cher?

15:17.480 --> 15:19.281
Yes!

15:19.283 --> 15:21.200
Oh, my God, that's perfect!

15:21.234 --> 15:23.252
Plus, they were great
friends after their breakup,

15:23.286 --> 15:24.353
and you know, it's... it's just like us!

15:24.355 --> 15:26.655
Yeah, so totally like us! Yeah!

