- Hey, Mom.

16:14.587 --> 16:15.604
Oh, hey, Riles.

16:15.606 --> 16:17.406
Ever hear the expression,

16:17.457 --> 16:20.509
"Two is company, three is a pathetic
girl dressed as Cher with no partner"?

16:21.528 --> 16:22.444
Tucker?

16:24.531 --> 16:26.381
What are you doing?

16:26.383 --> 16:29.284
I found this costume on the couch.

16:29.286 --> 16:31.437
Figured it was the perfect
way to get past security.

16:31.471 --> 16:34.189
Don't you work here?

16:34.224 --> 16:36.325
Oh. Oh, when I'm done with this show,

16:36.359 --> 16:38.627
nobody is gonna work here.

16:38.661 --> 16:39.628
Okay?

16:39.662 --> 16:42.181
It's time I got my dignity back.

16:47.637 --> 16:49.571
Hey, Mary. It's me, Jason.

16:51.591 --> 16:53.475
What are you doing here?

16:53.477 --> 16:55.410
