17:32.582 --> 17:34.383
unless you want this to get out too.

17:34.434 --> 17:36.368
You know he deserves it.

17:36.402 --> 17:37.486
He does everything to please you

17:37.537 --> 17:39.471
and all you've ever
done is crush his spirit.

17:39.506 --> 17:41.390
Fine.

17:41.441 --> 17:43.325
I actually need Tucker.

17:43.376 --> 17:46.278
His little revenge video
doubled the show ratings.

17:46.312 --> 17:48.197
So he can have his job back?

17:48.199 --> 17:49.181
Sure.

17:49.215 --> 17:50.315
Now put the mustache on

17:50.350 --> 17:53.585
and take me back to 1979.

17:56.673 --> 17:58.524
Okay, SweetHarts,

17:58.575 --> 18:00.158
