18:00.210 --> 18:01.159
Hey, hey.

18:01.194 --> 18:02.177
Where's your partner?

18:02.228 --> 18:03.478
Oh, he was just here.

18:03.513 --> 18:04.580
Sorry, couples only.

18:04.614 --> 18:06.415
