minute, he'll be right back.

18:08.051 --> 18:08.600
Rules are rules.

18:08.635 --> 18:11.453
- I swear.
- You two, you two, next.

18:11.455 --> 18:12.554
Riley, I am so sorry.

18:12.589 --> 18:14.306
Danny, come on! Hurry up.

18:14.357 --> 18:16.325
