going to make it up to you.

18:18.428 --> 18:20.379
Danny, come on! I gave you life!

18:20.413 --> 18:22.231
She's just giving you a hard time.

18:22.282 --> 18:24.333
- Can you give me a minute?
- No, Danny. It's fine. Not now.

18:24.367 --> 18:26.301
- Yeah, Danny. Not now.
